WEBVTT

00:13:59.132 --> 00:14:01.993
kama aibu ya kukaa
mbele ya televisheni,

00:14:02.898 --> 00:14:05.397
kuangalia Peter Jennings
akitangaza milenia mpya

00:14:05.421 --> 00:14:06.629
tena

00:14:06.653 --> 00:14:07.803
na tena

00:14:08.257 --> 00:14:09.407
na tena.

00:14:09.796 --> 00:14:11.146
Nilikua nimedanganywa,

00:14:12.084 --> 00:14:13.234
nimedhulumiwa,

00:14:13.696 --> 00:14:14.846
nimepumbazwa.

00:14:15.403 --> 00:14:18.477
Lakini wakati huu, mkombozi wa uongo
alikua mimi.

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:23.302
Unaona, nimepita njia ndefu
kutoka madhabahuni

00:14:23.326 --> 00:14:25.422
usiku niliodhani
dunia ingeisha,

00:14:26.371 --> 00:14:28.576
kwenye dunia ambayo watu wananena
kwa lugha

00:14:28.957 --> 00:14:31.955
na kuona mateso kama
kama tendo la lazima la Mungu